content:
You can now run a sequence of batch data transforms one after the other without scheduling by using a flow. After a batch data transform completes, the next one starts immediately.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This feature is available starting in June 2024.

How: To run batch data transforms consecutively, use the Run Batch Data Transform action in a flow.
title: Run Batch Data Transforms with No Downtime
